    • using

      @CanIgnoreReturnValue public final GroupResult.Builder using​(GroupResult instance)
      Fill a builder with attribute values from the provided GroupResult instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with those from the given instance. Absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
      Parameters:
      instance - The instance from which to copy values
      Returns:
      this builder for use in a chained invocation
